<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Achievements | Engineering Science</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #2563eb;
            --text: #1f2937;
            --bg: #ffffff;
            --light-bg: #f9fafb;
            --border: #e5e7eb;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: var(--text);
            background-color: var(--bg);
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }

        h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 10px; border-bottom: 4px solid var(--primary); display: inline-block; }
        h2 { font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--primary); margin-top: 40px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; }
        h3 { margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 1.2rem; }

        .section { margin-bottom: 30px; }
        
        /* Competition Styling */
        .award-item {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 15px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        }
        .award-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
        .award-name { font-weight: bold; }
        .award-year { color: #6b7280; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }

        /* Academic Block Styling */
        .academic-card {
            background: var(--light-bg);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-left: 5px solid var(--primary);
        }
        .academic-card ul { margin: 10px 0 0 20px; padding: 0; }
        .academic-card li { margin-bottom: 5px; }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .award-item { flex-direction: column; }
            .award-year { margin-top: 5px; font-size: 0.9rem; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <h1>Achievements</h1>
        <p>A record of academic excellence and technical competition success.</p>
    </header>

    <section class="section">
        <h2>🏆 Major Competition Wins</h2>
        
        <div class="award-item">
            <div class="award-name">BusTech Grand Challenge — 2nd Runner Up</div>
            <div class="award-year">2025</div>
        </div>

        <div class="award-item">
            <div class="award-name">National Robotics Competition — First Place</div>
            <div class="award-year">2023</div>
        </div>

        <div class="award-item">
            <div class="award-name">Global Robotic Games (Mobile Robotics IV) — First Place</div>
            <div class="award-year">2023</div>
        </div>

        <div class="award-item">
            <div class="award-name">Young Inventor’s Journal — Gold Award</div>
            <div class="award-year">2022</div>
        </div>

        <div class="award-item">
            <div class="award-name">Engineering Innovation Challenge — 1st Runner Up</div>
            <div class="award-year">2020</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="award-item">
            <div class="award-name">Indonesia International Applied Science Project Olympiad — Silver Award</div>
            <div class="award-year">2020</div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
        <h2>🎓 Academic Excellence</h2>

        <div class="academic-card">
            <h3>2025 Highlights</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Most Outstanding Performance</strong> (Level 2.2 Engineering Science)</li>
                <li><strong>Director’s List</strong></li>
                <li><strong>Module Prizes:</strong> Applied Math 3, Microcontroller & Interfacing, Physics 2</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="academic-card">
            <h3>2024 Highlights</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Most Outstanding Performance</strong> (Level 1.2 Engineering Science)</li>
                <li><strong>3rd Most Outstanding Performance</strong> (Level 2.1 Engineering Science)</li>
                <li><strong>Director’s List</strong></li>
                <li><strong>Module Prizes:</strong> Physics 1, Applied Math 2A, Analogue Electronics</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="academic-card">
            <h3>2023 Highlights</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Most Outstanding Performance</strong> (Level 1.1 Engineering Science)</li>
                <li><strong>Director’s List</strong></li>
                <li><strong>Module Prizes:</strong> Applied Math 1, Electrical Engineering, Engineering & Society, Mechanical Engineering</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
        <h2>🏅 Additional Honors</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>SST Book Prize (Mathematics & Electronics)</li>
            <li>SUTD-SST-NP Big D Camp — Design Excellence Award</li>
            <li>Singapore and Asian Schools Math Olympiad — Gold & Silver</li>
            <li>Australian Mathematics Competition — Distinction</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

</body>
</html>
